<P>To S^r Alexander Cairnes of <HI>Monaghan</HI> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="OXF" EXTENT="1+ letters">n the Kingdom of Ireland Baronet <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="OXF" EXTENT="1 letter">his Repre&s;entation of a Turki&s;h Funeral is Re&s;pectfully Dedicated.</P>
</FIGURE></P>
